Live and Let Die star Jane Seymour, 71, took to Instagram to share a snap that left her 252,000 followers gobsmacked. The Hollywood actress shared a picture of herself sporting a short platinum blonde wig, while holding a cigar. She posed in a rustic leather jacket and tight skinny jeans. The actress also wore heavy eye make-up and accessorised with a large black pendant. She captioned the snap: "A little behind-the-scenes shot of Addison Walker! Have you seen ‘The Guardians of Justice’ yet on @netflix?" Many social media users rushed to the comments to compliment the actress on her phenomenal new look. Brandon.joseph.sandoval said: "Wow, you look amazing!" Michaela_quinn_medicine_woman added: "I love it! You are so beautiful Jane!"